{"id":"4648","user":{"id":"102024","nickname":"tc","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/FkFGmkSmcMZQ8CmNmAEjrtwJBQoC","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"title":"【算法挑战】神灵的密码","content":"<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FnJ26epshJpabJC_ax1rIPym_In4\">\n<font size=\"1\">本次素材来源：史蒂夫三兄弟</font>\n<br>\n<p>传送中，MC世界的三位神灵掌握着三个数字的密码，如果能解开这三个数字秘密的训练师就能通过他们的考验：</p>\n<p>战斗之神掌握着数字a,</p>\n<p>魔法之神掌握着数字b,<br></p>\n<p>永生之神掌握着数字c,</p>\n<p>a,b,c是三个自然数，</p>\n<p>a &lt; b &lt; c，</p>\n<p>并满足：a x a + b x b = c x c</p>\n<p>例如，3 x 3 + 4 x 4 = &nbsp;5 x 5 &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n<p>而且：a + b + c = 1000</p>\n<p>这三个数的的乘积a x b x c 的结果就是密码。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><iframe src=\"https://ide.codemao.cn/we/770701\" width=\"640\" height=\"498\"></iframe></p>\n<p>难度：两星</p>\n<p>（推荐使用box平台上的“快速循环”模块来解决，当然用2D编程猫的重复循环也可以，就是要等一段时间）</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FqfDnmtLyNL0NYm5LgTAs_Q4eK7P\"><br></p>\n<p>（P.S 这样的a,b,c在数学上被称为毕达哥拉斯三元组）</p>\n<p>尝试挑战一下吧，有任何问题直接留言就行。</p></p>","board_id":"7","board_name":"灌水池塘","updated_at":1498955655,"created_at":1498895964,"n_views":378,"n_replies":27,"n_comments":2,"is_authorized":false,"is_featured":false,"is_hotted":false,"is_pinned":false,"tutorial_flag":0,"ask_help_flag":0}